00:17:48.270 --> 00:17:49.270
Or Poverty.

00:17:49.270 --> 00:17:50.270
Poverty in America.

00:17:50.270 --> 00:17:55.460
Please join me in welcoming Tavis Smiley and
Cornel West to talk about "The Rich and The

00:17:55.460 --> 00:17:57.140
Rest of Us."

00:17:57.140 --> 00:17:58.630
[applause]

00:17:58.630 --> 00:18:06.200
&gt;&gt;Stacy: They, we have a video that we wanna
show.

00:18:06.200 --> 00:18:07.200
